Hercules;;76;;84;;G;;Disney tackles Greek mythology in this animated feature. Hercules (Tate Donovan), a son of gods, was snatched as a baby by Hades (James Woods) and forced to live among mortals as a half-man, half-god. Now a teenager, Hercules needs to perform a rite of passage on Earth to prove himself worthy of living with the gods on Mount Olympus. With his plucky satyr sidekick, Philoctetes (Danny DeVito), along for the ride, Hercules must learn how to use his strength to defeat a series of evil creatures.;;Animation,Adventure,Kids & family;;Ron Clements,John Musker;;1997;;Tate Donovan,Josh Keaton,Roger Bart,Danny DeVito,James Woods,Susan Egan,Bobcat Goldthwait,Matt Frewer,Rip Torn,Samantha Eggar,Barbara Barrie,Hal Holbrook,Paul Shaffer,Amanda Plummer,Carole Shelley,Charlton Heston;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hercules